text: Stadion Miejski w Tychach (English: Municipal Stadium in Tychy) is a football stadium located in Tychy, Poland. It is the home ground of GKS Tychy. The stadium holds 15,300 people. ==See also== *List of football stadiums in Poland ==External links== * Stadion Miejski w Tychach ==References== Category:Sports venues completed in 2015 Category:Buildings and structures in Tychy Category:2015 establishments in Poland Category:Football venues in Poland Category:Sports venues in Silesian Voivodeship Category:GKS Tychy
